{"tid":1418130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇和理非遊行","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:06:55.000Z","uid":67645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f4828d1bfc50d1044ad72e9fb3f6675678db2363","tid":1418130,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"好多人都話要再搞大遊行<br />\n其實個問題係政府唔會俾你地和理非<br />\n當一人多行出馬路就話你非法集結之後就開你波<br />\n<br />\n雖然支持嘅人愈黎愈多<br />\n但係上街表態嘅人就愈黎愈少<br />\n<br />\n真正和理非除左遊行之外<br />\n仲可以搞和平集會<br />\n例如機場、又或者老人家最鐘意嘅維園晚會<br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅工作係要令多啲人支持，同時佢地會以行動表態<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86b5ab88ca48bef8e84f174fb217b31ddc4ade0","tid":1418130,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e891ee5b4236f7673f86d05eb3d6a3466386293","tid":1418130,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上去"},{"pid":"cc6ae859efb15c27e1122034b43a453844fdadc2","tid":1418130,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:59.000Z","msg":"打就要打要害<br />\n<br />\n民航署一手料：政府要冷處理機場罷工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411641</a><br />\n<br />\n[機場防線] 再咁落去我地無可能贏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414005</a><br />\n<br />\n[會師機場]今日7區完左就全世界入機場！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412731</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］機場開始多人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412505</a><br />\n<br />\n隻字不提機場 大家識做啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412111</a><br />\n<br />\n玩咗咁多個場..最好都係everyday和你飛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390555</a>"},{"pid":"88ff4a139ca182313a056f1e7f46cb9e5b716dce","tid":1418130,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"和理非都要諗對策<br />\n要對應政權嘅招<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a458733c2cbd0f33ec3a3b22caef99e3c19c476","tid":1418130,"uid":299468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得係時候比勇武休息一下<br />\n從經濟入手<br />\n一係機場機會 成本低效率高<br />\n涼下冷氣 警察又無藉口清場<br />\n外國旅客繼續睇到黑警真面目<br />\n二來罷工 機場職員 巴士地鐵司機 公務員都係重要人物"},{"pid":"ea45474f5db0b406b08e2b1129d6ca947388b4bc","tid":1418130,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a458733c2cbd0f33ec3a3b22caef99e3c19c476","tid":1418130,"uid":299468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得係時候比勇武休息一下<br />\n從經濟入手<br />\n一係機場機會 成本低效率高<br />\n涼下冷氣 警察又無藉口清場<br />\n外國旅客繼續睇到黑警真面目<br />\n二來罷工 機場職員 巴士地鐵司機 公務員都係重要人物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"長期勇武一定唔掂<br />\n更何況我地又唔係真係武裝革命<br />\n以往所講嘅和理非-&gt;勇武loop都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n和理非一定要有新對策<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo